{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Do not apply income tax to our statutory annual holiday pay",
        "additional_details": "I believe that If income tax was removed from employees' holiday pay, it would be a vote winner and also encourage more people into employment reducing the Government's astronomical cost for universal credit each year.",
        "background": "I want the Government to introduce a law to prevent income tax being applied to employees' statutory holiday pay.",
